# 4. Quick Network Test (Very Important)

VDI environments often have **internal routing**.

From macOS run:

```
nc -zv HOSTNAME 8471
```

or

```
telnet HOSTNAME 8471
```

Important IBM i ports:

| Port | Purpose        |
| ---- | -------------- |
| 8471 | database       |
| 8475 | remote command |
| 8476 | data queue     |
| 8470 | signon         |

If these ports fail from mac → it's **network segmentation**.

